ity, we can envision a\nquantum network of BECs coupled via cavity-mediated interactions in non-trivial\ngeometries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Dec 2017 16:08:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Jun 2018 07:31:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-28"}
