her study and calibration of\nthe BF effect in realistic images will be crucial.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Dec 2017 19:36:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 May 2018 19:29:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 14 May 2018 22:34:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-16"}
