s, namely, Bangla, Devanagari and Gurumukhi, and the\ncorresponding results are reported.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Dec 2017 13:12:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 28 Jan 2018 15:10:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-06"}
