retion disk provides a realiable scenario. On the other hand, the narrow\nemission lines can be due to the presence of photoionized matter around the\naccreting source.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Dec 2017 13:33:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-07"}
