 Fe3+ impurity ions, namely the electron transfer from the\n5d1 excited levels of Ce3+ to Fe3+ was directly detected by EPR.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Dec 2017 13:44:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-09"}
